<%
  type_label = if @commitment.is_policy?
                 "Policy"
               elsif @commitment.is_calendar_event?
                 "Event"
               else
                 "Commitment"
               end
%>
# <%= type_label %> Settings

Current settings for <%= type_label.downcase %> **<%= @commitment.title %>**:

| Setting | Value |
|---------|-------|
| Title | <%= @commitment.title %> |
| Description | <%= @commitment.description || "(none)" %> |
| Critical Mass | <%= @commitment.critical_mass || "(none)" %> |
| Deadline | <%= @commitment.deadline %> |
<% if @commitment.is_calendar_event? %>
| Starts at | <%= @commitment.starts_at %> |
| Ends at | <%= @commitment.ends_at %> |
| Location | <%= @commitment.location || "(none)" %> |
<% end %>
